I’m online now! I’ll send you a local file, only .mp3 files will work. Make a “Spotify” folder on your computer, and drop any songs you want on Spotify into that folder as MP3 files. Open Spotify on your computer, click your name in the top right, hit settings, scroll down until you see “local files” and switch it to on, then under that button an option will appear where it’ll ask what files it can access for music. Click your new Spotify folder. A playlist will be created on your computer called “local files”. Add the songs from it to a new playlist (I just called mine oc unreleased). Open your phone, go to that new playlist, make sure the phone and computer on on the same Wi-Fi, and hit the little offline/download button at the top of the playlist. I know that’s a long list, just being thorough! Lemme know any songs you want on there I have a good list of files!
